            "chapterTitle": "Prohibition of Cruelty",
            "urn": 1624060,
            "body": "<p>Ibn 'Umar (May Allah be pleased with them) reported: The Prophet (\ufdfa) said, \"The expiation for beating or slapping a slave on the face for something he has not done is to set him free.\"<br/><br/><b>[Muslim]</b>.<br/><br/></p>",
